Licenses

The establishment has received an official license from the Canadian Gaming Commission. All necessary information about registration and licensing can be found on the official website, or you can make a request through the technical support service.

Security NB Casino Hotel

To ensure that all visitors can enjoy a relaxing and exciting holiday, the casino has organized a comprehensive protection and security system. Therefore, there is always a security service at the entrance, and other specialists monitor the behavior of visitors inside the casino.

In order to become a full member of the club, you will need to register, present documents, and confirm your age. An additional protective measure is the dress code. This makes it possible to exclude the appearance in the hall of people who are dressed inappropriately, or behave aggressively, and definitely, and interfere with other guests of a cultural holiday.

The casino has a serious video surveillance system. This is necessary in order to ensure the integrity of the gaming process and eliminate attempts at fraud on the part of clients and the dealers themselves. The Canadian casino strictly adheres to the policy of responsible, safe, and fair gaming.
